sep.gaia.resources

Interface LoaderEventListener<R extends DataResource>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - Type of the resources the information which availability implementing instances want to be informed about.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocationSearch, LocationWindow, POIManager, TileManager, WeatherCache, WeatherManager, WikipediaManager

    public interface LoaderEventListener<R extends DataResource>
    An interface for reacting if the corresponding loader has partially processed a query and therefore new data is avaliable.
    Author:
    Matthias Fisch

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onResourcesAvailable(java.util.Collection<R> resources)
      Will be called if the loader the implementation of this listener is assigned to, has partially processed a query.

        Will be called if the loader the implementation of this listener is assigned to, has partially processed a query.
        Parameters:
        resources - The loaded resources mixed with dummy-objects representing those not yet loaded.
